<aside class="atlas-help" aria-labelledby="atlas-help-heading">
  <h2 id="atlas-help-heading">How to read the Atlas</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Position groups projects by category and curated order; it does not rank their value.</li>
    <li>Every project node uses the same base size. Size does not indicate importance.</li>
    <li>Lines represent documented public relations only; their labels and patterns explain the relation type.</li>
    <li>The <a href="/work/">Work Register</a> provides the conventional complete list view at any time.</li>
  </ul>
</aside>
